OL,4,CUniversities could face fines over free
OL,5,Cspeech breaches
OL,6, Universities in England could face
OL,7, fines under new legislation if they
OL,8, fail to protect free speech on campus.
OL,10,FVisiting speakers, academics or
OL,11,Fstudents could seek compensation if
OL,12,Fthey suffer loss from a breach of a
OL,13,Funiversity's free speech obligations.
OL,15,FThe Higher Education (Freedom of Speech
OL,16,FBill) was one of the proposed pieces of
OL,17,Flegislation announced in the Queen's
OL,18,FSpeech on Tuesday.
OL,20,FUniversities said it was important not
OL,21,Fto create "unnecessary bureaucracy".
